image_analysis.description: A scanned page of a financial disclosure form titled 'Part 2: Filer's Employment Assets and Income'. The page is numbered 26 of 51 and lists several books authored by Donald J. Trump, detailing their publishers, income type (royalties), and income amounts.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with the filer's name and page number. The main body is a table with seven columns: '#', 'Description', 'EIF', 'attached schedule (Part 2 - EXHIBIT A) Reference #', 'Value', 'Income Type', and 'Income Amount'. A footer contains a note about an accompanying schedule and a document identifier in the bottom right corner.
